ural database of professionals working in a wide range of career fields who are willing to sponsor students to spend a day observing or shadowing them as they work ceas ma east asia summer internships for current ceas ma students summer internship opportunities based in asia may be available undergraduate summer asian internships through bing overseas studies program bosp supports internship positions in the people's republic of china hong kong taiwan japan republic of korea mongolia singapore and thailand the participating host institutions and specific internship job descriptions are available on bosp's website asia internships are open to all undergraduate students at stanford university each internship participant must commit to full time work a minimum of 35 hours per week for ten 10 weeks center for east asian studies stanford university 615 crothers way 100 encina commons stanford ca 94305 copyright 2009 site by aka
